title: Garmin City Navigator NT Europe 2014.10 Unlocked IMG
description:
Instructions:

1. If you are using SD-Card, rename it to Garmin.



2. Find a folder named Garmin on your Garmin Device or create New Folder and rename 

it to Garmin.



3. Copy downloaded gmapsupp.img to your Garmin Device to a folder named Garmin (at 

least 4GB free space required) or to your SD-card to the newly created folder called 

Garmin. or to your SD-Card (4GB card required).



4. Go to your Device's settings->map->mapinfo.



5. Select the mapset called Eurooppa.



6. All done! Enjoy!!!
